{"tid":401790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(日經) 一人一件搭小巴遇到嘅on9事","createTime":"2017-09-16T02:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T02:49:13.000Z","uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"516d0406b536753bee7f5bc6abdf55cb3ad1baf0","tid":401790,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"其實一次遇到幾個<br />\n<br />\n啱啱上車諗住坐後面<br />\n點知後面冇位<br />\n就咁樣遲疑咗半秒<br />\n後面條死港女就jip咗我一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個司機又好似食咗藥咁<br />\n乘客上車都唔係特別慢<br />\n但佢一開始已經好唔耐煩話: 有位你就坐啦<br />\n然後一路上不斷砵9前面啲車<br />\n但明明係佢痴住前面架車行<br />\n應該一秒行車距離都冇<br />\n仲要見到佢爬頭嗰陣同俾佢砵完個司機互啤咗一下<br />\n<br />\n最後有對情侶分開咗坐<br />\n男嘅坐我隔離，女嘅坐我前面<br />\n咁佢地堅持要講野阻住我訓都算<br />\n佢地互相叫對方 阿b 都唔到我理<br />\n但條仔中途無啦啦拎出一枝蚊怕水係撚咁噴，我就真係屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要噴你唔撚上車前噴<br />\n宜家係架車有蚊咩<br />\n噴撚到成車都係嗰陣味on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6dd3ebc2c893df64937b822f93da1d2f2d2798","tid":401790,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"生得太高，成日落車撞到頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伸脷，一米九二"},{"pid":"a0087cc6a7f4735acf4b8223077e2e18580e8833","tid":401790,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生得太高，成日落車撞到頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伸脷，一米九二</blockquote><br />\n咁巴士咪撞到仆街？"},{"pid":"e2c2d3467c65a42a50de1818669f021145a94d98","tid":401790,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生得太高，成日落車撞到頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fr