faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我知喇 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59dd86f8a723ad0cd340f3ab88a77d9b35d8a83","tid":401790,"uid":76112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:36:18.000Z","msg":"落車嗰陣個小巴佬竟然屌鳩我嗌有落，而唔係㩒鐘(架小巴有裝)<br />\n差啲想屌返佢&quot;咁你揸巴士啦柒頭&quot;<br />\n不過嗰陣着緊校服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔咁多年我都唔明佢點解屌我"},{"pid":"daa8d8d9fe15c693d4a3be5eb0d6bfe68c71f865","tid":401790,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:37:07.000Z","msg":"大大聲播錄音"},{"pid":"345a0dee815c62285cd7f82c9560007a77b226ee","tid":401790,"uid":11288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:41:36.000Z","msg":"小巴有企位 好on9"},{"pid":"c3a73a587f955f88eeafb55c5a8ffe0223564010","tid":401790,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"日日果個時間坐小巴都會撞到果個呀嬸<br />\n咁我日日都係果個站嗌有落，<br />\n咁佢又係果個站落既<br />\n<br />\n咁早幾個禮拜我有野買就過幾個站先落過<br />\n過左平時果個站個呀嬸碌大隻眼望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問我仲咩唔嗌有落搞到佢過左站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識嗌有落學咩人坐小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc84746ed1074f2d8111cfd77137b3132601f9f","tid":401790,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日果個時間坐小巴都會撞到果個呀嬸<br />\n咁我日日都係果個站嗌有落，<br />\n咁佢又係果個站落既<br />\n<br />\n咁早幾個禮拜我有野買就過幾個站先落過<br />\n過左平時果個站個呀嬸碌大隻眼望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問我仲咩唔嗌有落搞到佢過左站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識嗌有落學咩人坐小巴<img src=\"/